snippet.title: GHPC May 2021 update teaser: A Thousand Words
snippet.description:
The latest update to "Gunner, HEAT, PC!" adds US tanker voices! All in-game clips shown have their original audio without editing.

For more info, check out https://www.gunnerheatpc.com​​

GHPC is made possible by tank and sim gaming community members like you! To support the project: https://www.patreon.com/GunnerHEATPC​​ 

Trailer by TheBeastFeast
Music by Majoris: https://soundcloud.com/majoriss
